      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant. This specimen boasts a flawless Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The double VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency, and the rear subframe has been ultrasonically tested with zero signs of fatigue. Maintaining its original suspension geometry and factory-cross-drilled rotors, this vehicle exhibits zero mechanical parasitic loss and delivers a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. An uncompromising example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and chassis integrity.",
